Sound Player for the DS(i)

Requirements:

 - devkitPro           http://sourceforge.net/projects/devkitpro/files
 - devkitARM           http://sourceforge.net/projects/devkitpro/files/devkitARM
 - libnds              http://sourceforge.net/projects/devkitpro/files/libnds
 - tremor-lowmem-arm   http://sourceforge.net/projects/devkitpro/files/portlibs
 - libhelix 	       http://sourceforge.net/projects/devkitpro/files/portlibs

Make targets:

 all:     Builds sound libraries and NDS executable
 clean:   Removes everything in 'build' directory and the resulting NDS and ELF files
 clobber: Same as clean, but additionally performs 'make clean' on sound libraries

